44
00:04:47,900 --> 00:04:48,420
Ji Shu.

45
00:04:51,580 --> 00:04:52,850
Why are you with her?

46
00:04:53,780 --> 00:04:54,909
It's a coincidence.

47
00:04:55,900 --> 00:04:57,900
