60
00:05:45,060 --> 00:05:45,860
Use mine.

61
00:05:46,300 --> 00:05:47,100
Wait a minute.

62
00:05:47,420 --> 00:05:47,750
Okay.

63
00:05:47,900 --> 00:05:48,620
Song Yanqi.

64
00:05:48,820 --> 00:05:50,420
We haven't seen Ji Shu for a long time.

65
00:05:50,420 --> 00:05:51,480
We want to catch up.

66
00:05:51,740 --> 00:05:54,400
I'm afraid it's inconvenient for you to be here.

67
00:05:55,380 --> 00:05:56,020
Mr. Ji.

68
00:05:56,659 --> 00:05:58,180
Am I interrupting you?

69
00:05:58,620 --> 00:05:58,940
No.

70
00:06:02,700 --> 00:06:03,260
Ji Shu.

71
