healthy?

104
00:07:42,220 --> 00:07:43,659
Qi, I only brought three.

105
00:07:43,900 --> 00:07:44,700
Sorry.

106
00:07:45,420 --> 00:07:46,150
Ji Shu, here.

107
00:07:46,860 --> 00:07:48,320
