Since you want to give it to me,

114
00:08:04,100 --> 00:08:04,970
I'll take it.

115
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:10,580
Don't eat too much cold food.

116
00:08:10,580 --> 00:08:11,980
It's bad for your health.

117
00:08:14,380 --> 00:08:15,910
Thank you for your concern.

118
00:08:24,380 --> 00:08:25,180
So ugly.

119
00:08:25,740 --> 00:08:27,940
You look like a kitten eating secretly.

120
00:08:28,540 --> 00:08:29,500
You're ugly.

121
00:08:30,170 --> 00:08:30,740
Stop it.

122
00:08:30,780 --> 00:08:31,940
It's embarrassing

123
00:08:32,299 --> 00:08:33,360
in front of others.

124
00:08:34,539 --> 00:08:35,780
What are you doing?

125
00:08:36,179 --> 00:08:38,179
Now you have really become a kitten.

126
00:08:38,539 --> 00:08:40,870
Let me take you to wash up over there, okay?

127
00:08:41,659 --> 00:08:42,299
Okay.

128
00:08:42,340 --> 00:08:43,179
Let's go.

129
00:08:44,980 --> 00:08:45,780
Are you angry?

130
00:08:50,180 --> 00:08:51,110
Do you want some?

131
00:08:51,500 --> 00:08:53,430
I'm not eating. You can have it all.

132
00:08:54,340 --> 00:08:54,940
Is it good?

133
00:08:56,340 --> 00:08:56,780
Wait.

134
00:08:59,820 --> 00:09:01,080
You got it on your lips.

135
00:09:05,780 --> 00:09:06,700
What are you doing?

136
00:09:06,700 --> 00:09:07,220
Come on.

137
00:09:10,220 --> 00:09:12,660
They didn't need to do that.

138
00:09:14,100 --> 00:09:16,130
Why were they showing off their love?

139
00:09:16,130 --> 00:09:16,940
Why bother?

140
00:09:17,300 --> 00:09:18,940
It's almost written on her face

141
00:09:18,940 --> 00:09:19,860
that she has lived a better life

142
00:09:19,860 --> 00:09:21,390
after breaking up with you.

143
00:09:24,780 --> 00:09:25,340
Mr. Ji.

144
00:09:25,780 --> 00:09:26,840
As the saying goes,

145
00:09:26,980 --> 00:09:28,460
there are other fish in the sea.

146
00:09:28,460 --> 00:09:30,180
Why waste the whole forest

147
00:09:30,380 --> 00:09:31,710
for a crooked neck tree?

148
00:09:33,460 --> 00:09:35,580
No wonder he wrote a supporting character like that.

149
00:09:35,580 --> 00:09:37,440
He is like writing about himself.

150
00:09:37,740 --> 00:09:40,200
People who are named Ji Shu are so miserable.

151
00:09:40,700 --> 00:09:41,760
You think too much.

152
00:09:42,220 --> 00:09:43,620
You are just reluctant to admit it.

153
00:09:43,620 --> 00:09:45,220
Alright, I thought too much.

154
00:09:46,300 --> 00:09:46,820
Mr. Ji.

155
00:09:47,060 --> 00:09:48,380
I brought barbecue tools and ingredients.

156
00:09:48,380 --> 00:09:49,580
Do you want barbecue?

157
00:09:50,060 --> 00:09:52,790
-Oh you want it? Then I'll grill some for you.
-No.

158
00:10:09,100 --> 00:10:09,830
Here, Mr. Ji.

159
00:10:10,020 --> 00:10:11,420
I just grilled it. Try it.

160
00:10:11,860 --> 00:10:13,660
Thank you. I don't eat barbecue.

161
00:10:13,860 --> 00:10:14,320
Well...

162
00:10:14,980 --> 00:10:17,300
The barbecue contains heterocyclic amine and benzopyrene.

163
00:10:17,300 --> 00:10:18,490
There are cancer-causing risks.

164
00:10:18,490 --> 00:10:19,820
Ji Shu never eats these.

165
00:10:20,460 --> 00:10:21,900
We can't talk about the amount of toxicity aside from the dosage.

166
00:10:21,900 --> 00:10:22,890
It's okay to eat it once in a while.

167
00:10:22,890 --> 00:10:24,220
Ji Shu doesn't eat that.

168
00:10:27,180 --> 00:10:29,060
What's wrong with eating it occasionally?

169
00:10:29,060 --> 00:10:29,860
Song Yanqi.

170
00:10:30,050 --> 00:10:31,140
A person's lifestyle

171
00:10:31,140 --> 00:10:31,940
won't change.

172
00:10:32,130 --> 00:10:33,190
So what if he tries?

173
00:10:36,300 --> 00:10:38,360
Don't make yourself feel so wronged.

174
00:10:38,450 --> 00:10:40,340
You need to learn to fight fire with fire

175
00:10:40,340 --> 00:10:41,740
to stimulate her inner jealousy,

176
00:10:41,740 --> 00:10:42,650
and let her know that she cares about you

177
00:10:42,650 --> 00:10:43,980
so she'll be regretful.

178
00:10:44,820 --> 00:10:45,220
You...

179
00:10:48,260 --> 00:10:49,390
How is it? Is it good?

180
00:10:50,860 --> 00:10:51,340
Not bad.

181
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:52,420
Not bad, right?

182
00:10:52,540 --> 00:10:54,140
I'll grill some more for you.

183
00:10:58,740 --> 00:10:59,650
I want a drink.

184
00:10:59,940 --> 00:11:00,670
The iced one.

185
00:11:00,900 --> 00:11:02,300
It's bad for your health.

186
00:11:02,300 --> 00:11:03,100
I just want it.

187
00:11:04,860 --> 00:11:05,190
Okay.

188
00:11:06,860 --> 00:11:07,660
Wait a moment.

189
00:11:11,300 --> 00:11:11,780
Ji Shu,

190
00:11:12,460 --> 00:11:13,920
I want to talk to you alone.

191
00:11:31,740 --> 00:11:33,670
His ex-girlfriend is so powerful.

192
00:11:34,740 --> 00:11:36,400
Don't give her the copyright.

193
00:11:48,300 --> 00:11:48,980
Mr. Ji,

194
00:11:49,300 --> 00:11:51,140
