195
00:11:51,140 --> 00:11:52,260
I'm not interested.

196
00:11:52,260 --> 00:11:52,940
Take them away.

197
00:11:52,940 --> 00:11:54,870
But you just said it was delicious.

198
00:11:55,180 --> 00:11:56,110
Don't follow me.

199
00:11:59,140 --> 00:12:00,340
Do you want barbecue?

200
00:12:01,580 --> 00:12:02,580
What's wrong?

201
00:12:17,820 --> 00:12:18,480
Song Yanqi.

202
00:12:18,660 --> 00:12:19,860
Are you following me?

203
00:12:25,340 --> 00:12:27,070
I didn't follow you on purpose.

204
00:12:27,300 --> 00:12:28,250
I was worried

205
00:12:28,250 --> 00:12:29,510
