206
00:12:29,980 --> 00:12:30,510
I'm fine.

207
00:12:36,420 --> 00:12:38,340
Mr. Ji, I'm in a bad mood.

208
00:12:38,700 --> 00:12:40,010
I may not be able to

209
00:12:40,010 --> 00:12:41,470
get the copyright anyway.

210
00:12:41,620 --> 00:12:44,020
Why don't we find something to do and relax?

211
00:12:44,540 --> 00:12:45,870
What are you going to do?

212
00:12:46,460 --> 00:12:47,340
Come with me.

213
00:12:55,020 --> 00:12:56,860
